title: Luminator
info:
All the lovely music from the Australian demoparty "Flashback 2013".
As always the songs has been recorded from real hardware:
Commodore 64 SID 8580R5
Commodore 64 SID 6581R4AR
No normalizing, EQ, Compressor or Phase corrections! Just straight from the C-64er to the computer.
(D)2013 Dees Productions
